Nice thought, but Base1 just lists the damage base (before it goes into the calculations.<br>
<br>
If you look, Strike of Solusek is -2740, and Barrier of Force is +1.  Now, if negative numbers move you up the hate list, that would mean that clicking your epic would actually move you DOWN the hate list. And we know thats not true.  I don't believe that aggro is stored client-side at all. <br>
